        <Parent_String>transportation spaces [300122438], open spaces by function [300129929], open spaces [300008072], Open Spaces and Site Elements (hierarchy name ) [300139081], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
